HEADWORD: Salacious
<hw>Sa*la"cious</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>salax</ets>, <ets>-acis</ets>, fond of leaping, lustful, fr.
<ets>salire</ets> to leap. See <er>Salient</er>.]</ety> <def>Having a
